{
  "texts": [
    "Murugesan et al. [106] noted a 20% reduction in chloride diffusion coefficient and a 10% increase in resistance to carbonation.",
    "Singh et al. [103] found that a 10% SCBA replacement reduces porosity by 10% and enhances resistance to chloride penetration by 12%.",
    "Jha et al. [107] highlighted that SCBA improves sulfate resistance by 15% at a 10% replacement level and reduces water absorption.",
    "Rajasekar et al. [108] and Zareei et al.",
    "[109] reported similar benefits, including a 20% reduction in permeability, up to 20% improved sulfate resistance, and reduced water absorption."
  ]
}